路面污染泥土，并对辖区进行全面排查，查找类似情况，主动帮助村民做好路面泥土清理。 感谢社会各界的关注和理解! 辛口镇人民政府 2021 年 10 月 18 日 近日，天津西青，秋收车辆上路因车轮带泥被罚引发关注。辛口镇种植户徐先生称，玉米抢收第一天就被执法大队挡住并罚款 12000 多元，并要求上路车辆必须按照工地标准，对车轮进行清洗，出地路面铺上红毯才能收割。18 日，西青区城管局工作人员称，事情正在调查中，辛口镇执法部门不是自己的直属单位；辛口镇政府工作人员称，领导正在开会研究处理此事，届时会发通报。（北京头条）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-dea1608994848e0d79a5b0f0189d4a8c_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "311 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493101460"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8smUxfbk1sI0EAMaCDcxODU5NTg0IIjOtIsGMBE4jAJAEXIJNDkzMTAxNDYweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1634735977.8640754", "card_id": "Q_493017090", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 138}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么「百亿票房」演员中前十位一个女演员都没有？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "反映了目前行业创作的哪些问题？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-0e116ca0ace2b3a684521af013d9e4f7_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "305 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493017090"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8smUxfbk1sI0EAMaCDcxODQwODEwIPWis4sGMCE48wNAEnIJNDkzMDE3MDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1634735977.864733", "card_id": "Q_486903361", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 282}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "室友认为苹果是轻薄本天花板，认为苹果芯片吊打英特尔，我该如何与他沟通？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-471e6cf2483301fd7e272d2c633e9408_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "274 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/486903361"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8smUxfbk1sI0EAMaCDcwNDgyNDQ2IPHNhIoGMBw44wJAE3IJNDg2OTAzMzYxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "h